==English==
===Adjective===
{{en-adj-er-y|glass|y}}
# Of or like [[glass]], in particular smooth and (partly) reflective.
# {{surfing}} [[absence|Absence]] of any [[chop]] on the water, making it smooth like glass.  [[swell|Swell]] creating [[break]]ing [[wave]]s may still be present (hopefully), ''glassy'' refers just to the absense of surface chop, not to complete [[flat]]ness.
===Usage notes===
The comparitive and superlative are not much used.  For the [[surfing]] sense they're not used (conditions are either glassy or not).

